OL,6,FA man who was driving nearly double
OL,7,Fthe speed limit and aggressively
OL,8,Fundertaking cars along the A3 in
OL,9,FSurrey has lost his licence.
OL,11,FThe grey Volkswagen was driving at
OL,12,Fspeed despite a temporary 50 miles per
OL,13,Fhour limit in place for roadworks.
OL,15,FA member of the Roads Policing Unit
OL,16,Fspotted the car travelling along the
OL,17,FEsher Bypass near Painshill and Cobham
OL,18,Fon Saturday 15 April 2023.
