OL,6,FThe vehicle was then seen tailgating a
OL,7,FVauxhall Corsa travelling at the speed
OL,8,Flimit, trying to force it out of the
OL,9,Fway by flashing its lights and driving
OL,10,Fclose behind it in an aggressive
OL,11,Fmanner.
OL,13,FWhen the Vauxhall Corsa moved into a
OL,14,Fnearside lane, the Volkswagen
OL,15,Faccelerated sharply again to 91 miles
OL,16,Fan hour.
OL,18,FIt then undertook a Mercedes at 100
OL,19,Fmiles an hour, before undertaking
OL,20,Fthree further vehicles at 107 miles
OL,21,Fper hour.
