OL,6,FSergeant Gary Lefort stopped the car,
OL,7,Fsaying he had seen enough to be
OL,8,Fconvinced that the driver posed a
OL,9,Fsignificant risk to public safety.
OL,11,FThe driver tried to justify his
OL,12,Fbehaviour by claiming that someone was
OL,13,Fchasing him and trying to run him off
OL,14,Fthe road, becoming agitated and
OL,15,Fconfrontational.
OL,17,FHe was reported for dangerous driving
OL,18,Fand was sentenced earlier this month
OL,19,Fat Guildford Magistrates' Court.
