OL,6,FSimpson was also ordered to pay costs
OL,7,Fand a victim surcharge of #199 and
OL,8,Fcomplete 200 hours of unpaid work.
OL,10,FPS Lefort said, "The manner of driving
OL,11,Fdisplayed by Andrew Simpson
OL,12,Fexemplifies exactly why Roads Policing
OL,13,FUnits utilise unmarked vehicles and
OL,14,Frobustly enforce Fatal 5 offences.
OL,16,F"I hope the sentence handed down by
OL,17,Fthe court serves as a deterrent for
OL,18,Fother drivers who may think of driving
OL,19,Fin such a manner on Surrey's roads."
